caption.title: Relationship between value profile of locations chosen and for how long time the respondent has lived in Höganäs municipality.
caption.p: The size of the respective compartment is proportional to the number of observations in the respective category. PLV = "Place valuer", MLS = "My life style", ENV = "Environmental", LCO = "The local community", BEA = "Beauty", MEC = "My economy". The graph is based on raw data before imputation (χ 2 = 11.90, n = 269, p = 0.035).
